mens.title: Lacoste Sweater
mens.subtitle: Men's Organic Cotton Crew Neck Sweater
mens.description: Complete your classic seasonal wardrobe with this crew neck sweater. This eco-responsible organic cotton jersey piece features contrasting details and ribbed finishes, as well as an iconic small green embroidered crocodile on the chest. For a warm and stylish cozy look, wear it with rolled-up chino pants and sneakers from the collection.
